    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "For sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good condition, perfect for anyone seeking a reliable and attractive daily driver. The exterior is in great shape overall, though it does show its history with a few minor surface scratches and small door dings consistent with its age. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major systems are functioning properly. The interior has been kept clean, with only light wear on the upholstery and floor mats. This is a dependable car that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
